Class TTOperationalStatusAlarmControl

java.lang.Object
  org.fosstrak.reader.rprm.core.mgmt.alarm.AlarmControl
      org.fosstrak.reader.rprm.core.mgmt.alarm.TTOperationalStatusAlarmControl

public class TTOperationalStatusAlarmControl
extends AlarmControl

This class extends AlarmControl to control alarms generated when a monitored model element of type OperationalStatus transitions to a new value. This type of alarm is called "transition triggered" (abbreviated "TT").

Parameters:
name - A unique identifier
enabled - Defines whether the Alarm is enabled
level - The Alarm level
suppressInterval - The minimum number of seconds that shall elapse before the next Alarm of the same type is generated
triggerFromState - The value of the monitored, OperationalStatus-valued, model element prior to the state transition which triggers the alarm
triggerToState - The value of the monitored, OperationalStatus-valued, model element immediately after the state transition which triggers the alarm
